The paper discusses the intersection of edge computing and AI, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also focuses on the development of an Open Framework for Edge Intelligence, which involves the use of AI techniques such as machine learning (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of developing such a framework, which falls under the category of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
